      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "This is an absolute showstopper! We are thrilled to offer this stunning classic in truly mint condition. It looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor, with every detail meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standard. If you\u2019ve been searching for a flawless example of this model, your search ends here\u2014this is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection!",
