    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for a functional car at an affordable price. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it has the typical sounds and minor leaks associated with a vehicle of this age and mileage. It has been recently serviced for basic maintenance, making it a dependable choice for commuting despite its cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 17500.0,
