    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in absolute showroom condition. This specimen has been meticulously curated and maintained to the highest standards, offering an uncompromising driving experience. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, preserved interior, reflects a level of care seldom seen in the pre-owned market. For the discerning collector or driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents the definitive choice in quality and value.",
