    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! It honestly breaks my heart a little to be posting this, but it's time for this absolute beauty to find a new home. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, pampered with the best products, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You might find a tiny, honest sign of love here or there if you really go looking, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come and runs like an absolute dream. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy those weekend cruises as much as I have. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
