      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level specimen featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six, meticulously maintained with a recently recalibrated VANOS system and verified compression across all cylinders. This chassis benefits from a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a bespoke suspension overhaul utilizing high-durometer bushings for zero-deflection handling. The 6-speed manual transmission offers surgical precision, paired with a lightweight flywheel for instantaneous throttle response. Every fluid circuit has been flushed and upgraded with high-thermal-capacity lubricants. This is a turn-key, mechanically optimized masterpiece designed for the purist who demands peak lateral grip and drivetrain transparency. Truly a museum-grade example with flawless power delivery.",
